"file_path":"/1p9bHEuVCvdUJHT22ToP64Fsc6A.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":0.667,"vote_average":0},{"width":960,"height":1440,"file_path":"/uL2B5wls8ZscQPsLKhl1jgx5vXa.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":0.667,"vote_average":0}],"backdrops":[{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/ux9bsXuwkhlSHwcnmKa8hzTOadO.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":3.334},{"width":1917,"height":1080,"file_path":"/6ykQysq6kfZ6Yw5C4dkhcZRd5QI.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":1.775,"vote_average":1.75},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/p23kiJvHLTEzVFYayGa3WqEluc1.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/7ImlbWiJcIsZx0xpN0nSSQF9xHF.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/jOiiloLKGhWpFQa1KJADjker0zH.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/9dkZz9uRDk7mNfoFNAqSKW5dCXV.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/1pTI4nkI2XnCuVVQRzIvVT7U6jC.jpg","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/iLuJK6HlhBQXdGl4VwP8gFTCzBT.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/7u6AZgDsmKdsV5wAR3u0HIQcwPV.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/3cH1aK9204DpizmM8joBe0XKlgM.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/9NPNJPxAXVdwWvqxRJ6HSrlkjFr.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/ygeDLVTwn7C87rbqaxDKo6zMx8n.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":721,"file_path":"/pddRG2e7Ytfjc09SE6zv3KW3d2o.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.775,"vote_average":0},{"width":2886,"height":1623,"file_path":"/4xN3phAX024b251CPhy8zvsXbBc.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":1,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T05:16:52.605+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":136,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"1900年的旧金山，一白人女子在唐人街被害，而嫌疑人正是一名华人男子，凶案引起社会震荡，民众纷纷要求取缔唐人街。中医秦福（刘昊然 饰）和华人阿鬼（王宝强 饰）卷入此案，他们与时间赛跑，在斗智斗勇之中，终于找到凶手。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Detective Chinatown 1900","runtime":135,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"In 1900, a white woman was murdered in Chinatown in San Francisco, and the suspect was a Chinese man. The murder caused social shock, and people demanded the closure of Chinatown."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"唐探 1900","runtime":135,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"在 1900 年的美國舊金山唐人街，華裔印第安獵人阿鬼（王寶強 飾）與留美青年秦福（劉昊然 飾）因一宗奇案偶然結識，誤打誤撞成為「唐人街神探」孖寶。沒想到該案件居然牽聯甚廣，甚至會影響唐人街以至全美國華人的命運…在「唐人街大佬」白軒齡（周潤發 飾）全力支持下，這對神探孖寶要爭分奪秒找出真相，過程中驚險萬分，同時爆發無窮歡樂！"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"In het San Francisco van de jaren 1900 wordt een blanke vrouw vermoord in Chinatown en de verdachte is een Chinese man. De moord veroorzaakt een sociale schok en het publiek roept op om Chinatown te verbieden. Chinese geneeskundebeoefenaar Qin Fu en de Chinese man Ghost zijn betrokken bij de zaak, en ze racen tegen de klok om de moordenaar te vinden te midden van een strijd van verstand en moed."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Detective Chinatown 1900","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"แก๊งม่วนป่วนอเมริกา","runtime":0,"tagline":"กลับมาฮาให้ม่วน กับภารกิจป่วนอเมริกา","homepage":"","overview":"ในช่วงปี 1900 ที่เมืองซานฟรานซิสโก หญิงผิวขาวถูกฆาตกรรมในย่านที่อยู่อาศัยของคนจีน และผู้ต้องสงสัยคือชายชาวจีน คดีนี้สร้างแรงสั่นสะเทือนให้สังคมจนประชาชนเรียกร้องให้สั่งปิดย่านที่อยู่อาศัยนี้ ต่อมา นักแพทย์แผนจีน ฉินฝู และชายชาวจีนที่เรียกตัวเองว่า โกสต์ ถูกดึงเข้าไปพัวพันกับคดีนี้ พวกเขาต้องแข่งกับเวลาเพื่อหาตัวฆาตกร ท่ามกลางการต่อสู้ด้วยสติปัญญาและความกล้าหาญ"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Detetive Chinatown: O Mistério de 1900","runtime":135,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://sato.tv.br/title/18417c97-722d-80db-b3d2-f7ee2204a231/","overview":"Chinatown, São Francisco, 1900. A filha de um congressista que odeia imigrantes asiáticos é assassinada e o principal suspeito é o filho de Bai Xuanling, homem de grande influência no bairro chinês. O crime revolta e joga a população da cidade contra os chineses, exigindo o fechamento do distrito. Para tentar salvar o filho e evitar a perseguição a seu povo, Bai Xuanling recorre ao jovem “mestre do raciocínio” Qin Fu, que se associa a Ah Gui, homem que chegou à cidade para vingar seu pai adotivo. Juntos, os dois tentam descobrir o que realmente aconteceu."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"唐探1900","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"1900年的舊金山，一白人女子在唐人街被害，而嫌疑人正是一名華人男子，兇案引起社會震盪，民眾紛紛要求取締唐人街。中醫秦福（劉昊然 飾）和華人阿鬼（王寶強 飾）捲入此案，他們與時間賽跑，在鬥智鬥勇之中，終於找到兇手。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Детектив из Чайнатауна, 1900 год","runtime":136,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Сан-Франциско, начало 1900-х годов. В Чайнатауне убита белая женщина, а главным подозреваемым становится китаец. Преступление вызывает широкий общественный резонанс, и горожане требуют закрыть китайский квартал. Расследованием дела занимаются врач традиционной китайской медицины Цинь Фу и китайско-индейский охотник по прозвищу А-Гуй."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Thám Tử Phố Tàu 1900","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Năm 1900, một phụ nữ da trắng đã bị sát hại tại khu phố Tàu ở San Francisco, và nghi phạm là một người đàn ông Trung Quốc. Vụ giết người đã gây chấn động xã hội và mọi người yêu cầu đóng cửa khu phố Tàu."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"당인가탐정1900","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"“탐정의 기원을 향한 시간 여행”  1900년, 미국 샌프란시스코의 차이나타운. 화려한 전당포가 아닌, 조촐한 거리 구석에서 한 사건이 모든 것을 바꾼다. 바로 한 고귀한 미국인의 딸이 끔찍하게 살해되고, 이 사건의 유일한 단서는 살해된 원주민 노인이었다. 강력한 정치적 압력과 혐오가 드리운 상황에서, 명문 한의사이자 수학 추리 천재인 진푸와 인디언 부족에서 자란 힘센 사냥꾼 아구이가 우연히 손을 잡고 ‘탐정 듀오’를 결성한다. 그들의 조사는 단순한 살인사건을 뛰어넘고, 대륙을 가로지르는 역사적 이슈—혁명, 인종차별, 정치 음모—까지 파고들게 되며, 유머와 긴장, 그리고 인간애가 동시에 빛나는 전개가 이어지는데..."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Detective Chinatown 1900","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En 1900, una mujer blanca fue asesinada en Chinatown, en San Francisco, y el sospechoso era un chino. El asesinato causó conmoción social y la gente exigió el cierre de Chinatown."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Kinų kvartalo detektyvas 1900","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Filmas, kurio veiksmas vyksta 1900-aisiais San Fransiske, pasakoja apie Qin Fu ir Ah Gui atliekamą tyrimą dėl baltaodės moters nužudymo Kinų kvartale."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"679ddaa1176fdb2244cb39ce","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/679ddaa1176fdb2244cb39ce","author":"CinemaSerf","content":"$11","created_at":"2025-02-01T08:26:09.684Z","updated_at":"2025-02-01T08:26:09.823Z","author_details":{"name":"CinemaSerf","rating":6,"username":"Geronimo1967","avatar_path":"/9HcQx0Yfbxy8eqr3ft66X9uWMf0.jpg"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":980477,"adult":false,"title":"Ne Zha 2","video":false,"overview":"After a catastrophic event leaves their bodies destroyed, Ne Zha and Ao Bing are granted a fragile second chance at life. As tensions rise between the dragon clans and celestial forces, the two must undergo a series of perilous trials that will test their bond, challenge their identities, and decide the fate of both mortals and immortals.","genre_ids":[16,14,12,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":28.7072,"vote_count":595,"poster_path":"/cb5NyNrqiCNNoDkA8FfxHAtypdG.jpg","release_date":"2025-01-29","vote_average":8.112,"backdrop_path":"/8btfz81bOJ2lC7cujYBTw03wzg3.jpg","original_title":"哪吒之魔童闹海","original_language":"zh"},{"id":931944,"adult":false,"title":"The Devil's Bath","video":false,"overview":"In 1750 Austria, a deeply religious woman named Agnes has just married her beloved, but her mind and heart soon grow heavy as her life becomes a long list of chores and expectations. Day after day, she is increasingly trapped in a murky and lonely path leading to evil thoughts, until the possibility of committing a shocking act of violence seems like the only way out of her inner prison.","genre_ids":[18,9648,36,27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0098,"vote_count":157,"poster_path":"/txVfrmwFOKB5qczM0ENYSqKMnSv.jpg","release_date":"2024-03-08","vote_average":6.573,"backdrop_path":"/9oD95lebaaSNQHnLTLjjfITaCg7.jpg","original_title":"Des Teufels Bad","original_language":"de"},{"id":1260951,"adult":false,"title":"Her Story","video":false,"overview":"Wang Tiemei, a single mother, loses her job and moves, befriending neighbor Xiaoye who appears cheerful but is depressed. Their bond grows as Tiemei navigates relationships with her ex-husband causing trouble.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2772,"vote_count":64,"poster_path":"/d19YpGra7LRMYnOZQi9Vbn1jjhB.jpg","release_date":"2024-11-09","vote_average":7.563,"backdrop_path":"/tVTI6OrkI1UtydLLEdKl0G2xNXS.jpg","original_title":"好东西","original_language":"zh"},{"id":472717,"adult":false,"title":"The Documentary","video":false,"overview":"D. stalks Sandra but she doesn't know it. She does think that D. is a documentary filmmaker having her be in film about conquering fear. Little does she know that D. is not who he claims to be, and far worse.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6903,"vote_count":77,"poster_path":"/g56xy5bCuVwD5IRV2MGlQXBEoD2.jpg","release_date":"2017-08-22","vote_average":6.3,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"D.","original_language":"en"},{"id":522811,"adult":false,"title":"The Accidental Detective 2: In Action","video":false,"overview":"A comic book storekeeper, Dae-man, and the legendary homicide detective, Tae-su, who met on previous case quit their jobs to open a private detective agency.","genre_ids":[35,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5259,"vote_count":40,"poster_path":"/tbXQWdfzEUUQJXhkieQwaQ4XAqf.jpg","release_date":"2018-06-13","vote_average":6.413,"backdrop_path":"/1kzsu5rW3xt4K96hXyooWAxBeVD.jpg","original_title":"탐정: 리턴즈","original_language":"ko"},{"id":1454800,"adult":false,"title":"Trapped","video":false,"overview":"In 1995, the year before the comprehensive gun ban policy was implemented, the tranquility of Mangya Town was shattered. A notorious bandit leader, who had hidden a massive treasure, broke out of prison. Forty-three ruthless outlaws gathered from all directions, joining their leader, Beishan, in blockading Mangya by force. The entire town was plunged into a desperate crisis—cut off from fuel and communication!\r The bandits wanted both money and lives. Gunfire erupted across Mangya as a massive sandstorm loomed on the horizon. Facing impossible odds—one gun against eighty-eight—the gang also turned on each other in a brutal \"dog-eat-dog\" power struggle. Surrounded by enemies, with sandstorms blotting out the sun and death hanging by a thread—how can they turn the tide?","genre_ids":[18,80,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.5463,"vote_count":16,"poster_path":"/mmIqkyXhlgcaSb1S8zJsLQwGBls.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-29","vote_average":7.313,"backdrop_path":"/mINSxREmed7uTom1HiradrnwYoP.jpg","original_title":"Trapped","original_language":"zh"},{"id":79382,"adult":false,"title":"I Wish","video":false,"overview":"Twelve-year-old Koichi, who has been separated from his brother Ryunosuke due to his parents' divorce, hears a rumor that the new bullet trains will precipitate a wish-granting miracle when they pass each other at top speed.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.827,"vote_count":173,"poster_path":"/jLsUvhEgovME7dI283nnjqArmwI.jpg","release_date":"2011-06-11","vote_average":7.275,"backdrop_path":"/oRqDdcxBvAWIBGq3z8wN6uOFNEZ.jpg","original_title":"奇跡","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1055110,"adult":false,"title":"Female Teacher Closing the Door","video":false,"overview":"A sensual suspense that tells the story of a female teacher and a young student locked in a closed room in the middle of summer.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.9896,"vote_count":20,"poster_path":"/731QvAm8kE0egoxn2oBoFijME2O.jpg","release_date":"2021-10-03","vote_average":5.4,"backdrop_path":"/vAAekmyeB9DpRKeJRZNbmIxoNKx.jpg","original_title":"扉を閉めた女教師","original_language":"ja"},{"id":83706,"adult":false,"title":"The Viral Factor","video":false,"overview":"Agent Jon contemplates leaving the force until he learns his brother is working as a mercenary for a former colleague who betrayed their team.","genre_ids":[28,80,53,18,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7267,"vote_count":110,"poster_path":"/7J0SlFWcVFdErk5Vaax35xb19de.jpg","release_date":"2012-01-19","vote_average":5.741,"backdrop_path":"/cvN2G6PJ8R5r5G2pPYnsyiNXWMh.jpg","original_title":"逆戰","original_language":"zh"},{"id":33194,"adult":false,"title":"Xiu Xiu: The Sent-Down Girl","video":false,"overview":"Young teen girl Xiu Xiu is sent away to a remote corner of the Sichuan steppes for manual labor in 1975 (sending young people to there was a part of Cultural Revolution in China). A year later, she agrees to go to even more remote spot with a Tibetan saddle tramp Lao Jin to learn horse herding.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9934,"vote_count":46,"poster_path":"/f60ZzxvcNjQG1aXomXuKWEzS2pP.jpg","release_date":"1998-02-19","vote_average":7.2,"backdrop_path":"/6XCGLN8Nb7Oa0AF41UtS0nUFN7l.jpg","original_title":"天浴","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1280330,"adult":false,"title":"Operation Hadal","video":false,"overview":"Mercenaries have occupied an offshore platform in Chinese territorial waters by force. The Chinese Navy sets sail to repel the invaders as the Jiao Long commando team prepares for a fierce fight in the deep sea.","genre_ids":[18,28,10752],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.9584,"vote_count":13,"poster_path":"/joALXjCQCKTSDREQEJxn83U4ORK.jpg","release_date":"2025-01-26","vote_average":7.462,"backdrop_path":"/wteoGPQwhj79yQuEINoTwqfEzav.jpg","original_title":"蛟龙行动","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1184222,"adult":false,"title":"A Long Shot","video":false,"overview":"Inspired by a shocking incident at a factory in northeastern China in the mid-90s, this astonishing debut film portrays people struggling amidst rapid changes in the status quo. The production of the gunfight in the latter part is superb.  A surprising directorial debut on a large scale.","genre_ids":[18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5115,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/8a7Hg3b3dwf45TsEmQmewIvmbQ8.jpg","release_date":"2024-11-01","vote_average":5.875,"backdrop_path":"/h1JwhsRFDsUiCnMt8TWEX02OGl3.jpg","original_title":"老枪","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1224228,"adult":false,"title":"Shukberta - Pentagon Flying Saucer","video":false,"overview":"","genre_ids":[16,35,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1097,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/mSsvBQTFzuU3vmhlo7ShQUdqaMq.jpg","release_date":"2023-12-30","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/38WQYXMPYhMuregxcZqlKQ1k6pk.jpg","original_title":"舒克贝塔·五角飞碟","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1056444,"adult":false,"title":"The Colors Within","video":false,"overview":"Totsuko is a high school student with the ability to see the 'colors' of others. Colors of bliss, excitement, and serenity, plus a color she treasures as her favorite. Kimi, a classmate at her school, gives off the most beautiful color of all. Although she doesn't play an instrument, Totsuko forms a band with Kimi and Rui, a quiet music enthusiast they meet at a used bookstore in a far corner of town. As they practice at an old church on a remote island, music brings them together, forming friendships and stirring affections.","genre_ids":[16,18,10402],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.8948,"vote_count":55,"poster_path":"/gOWDvzglcQZOQPqGfVF6hfOhMNT.jpg","release_date":"2024-08-30","vote_average":6.927,"backdrop_path":"/vmSyIJSc8froKqFEZHnsZGzdYCb.jpg","original_title":"きみの色","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1299537,"adult":false,"title":"Successor","video":false,"overview":"Ma Chenggang, a wealthy man in Xihong City, worries that his eldest son is too spoiled to succeed him. Determined to raise a capable successor, he takes an unconventional approach. They conceal their wealth, moving the family to a dilapidated neighborhood, and maintain an illusion of poverty, so that his son could develop qualities such as hard work, knowledge, careful budgeting, physical fitness, and perseverance.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.5657,"vote_count":82,"poster_path":"/jqGZEk4sLGGmIXBDQzxTuT1lZx2.jpg","release_date":"2024-07-13","vote_average":6.97,"backdrop_path":"/9ir1UZYWBZBkgCoRUIV0ffk43Xe.jpg","original_title":"抓娃娃","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1001006,"adult":false,"title":"Block Pass","video":true,"overview":"Friendship and rebellion - but how will a secret play out in the masculine world of motocross?  Willy and Jojo are best friends. They share a passion for motocross - whereas Willy uses it to honour his deceased father, it is only by excelling in the sport that Jojo’s father will notice him. Also the masculine world or racing is perfectly suited to suppress their own insecurities. Yet when Willy one fateful night discovers the hidden love life of Jojo, he will be forced to take sides in the wave of homophobia that follows.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8899,"vote_count":85,"poster_path":"/mVCsjlKa2wZV4uP8JJiHopkC4lG.jpg","release_date":"2025-02-05","vote_average":6.771,"backdrop_path":"/iaRyVMgHxbFEFIDQLCXmntmWLKl.jpg","original_title":"La Pampa","original_language":"fr"},{"id":4588,"adult":false,"title":"Lust, Caution","video":false,"overview":"During World War II, a secret agent must seduce and assassinate an official who works for the Japanese puppet government in Shanghai.","genre_ids":[28,18,10749,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.1274,"vote_count":777,"poster_path":"/6c1tqfJEBuIyhQC19SLlLQAUAvJ.jpg","release_date":"2007-09-24","vote_average":7.251,"backdrop_path":"/lU1fQews2gye23PocVE48CsTmOQ.jpg","original_title":"色‧戒","original_language":"zh"},{"id":974573,"adult":false,"title":"Another Simple Favor","video":false,"overview":"Stephanie and Emily reunite on the beautiful island of Capri, Italy for Emily's extravagant wedding to a rich Italian businessman. Along with the glamorous guests, expect murder and betrayal to RSVP for a wedding with more twists and turns than the road from the Marina Grande to the Capri town square.","genre_ids":[35,53,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.889,"vote_count":493,"poster_path":"/zboCGZ4aIqPMd7VFI4HWnmc7KYJ.jpg","release_date":"2025-03-07","vote_average":5.761,"backdrop_path":"/b6e5Nss2QNoQM4wJv2VppChswNP.jpg","original_title":"Another Simple Favor","original_language":"en"},{"id":535167,"adult":false,"title":"The Wandering Earth","video":false,"overview":"When the Sun begins to expand in such a way that it will inevitably engulf and destroy the Earth in a hundred years, united mankind finds a way to avoid extinction by propelling the planet out of the Solar System using gigantic engines, moving it to a new home located four light years away, an epic journey that will last thousands of years.","genre_ids":[878,28,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.1898,"vote_count":1108,"poster_path":"/z3MXFdFjrYmoxOEFgE1wuphwo2a.jpg","release_date":"2019-02-05","vote_average":6.6,"backdrop_path":"/wIrqeoJHYtZmneqIufPtcOHMjOg.jpg","original_title":"流浪地球","original_language":"zh"},{"id":1088514,"adult":false,"title":"The Room Next Door","video":false,"overview":"Ingrid and Martha were close friends in their youth, when they worked together at the same magazine. Ingrid went on to become an autofiction novelist while Martha became a war reporter, and they were separated by the circumstances of life. After years of being out of touch, they meet again in an extreme but strangely sweet situation.","genre_ids":[18,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.5423,"vote_count":661,"poster_path":"/qMibLyArrlBJ87AoqQBeVaFeRXp.jpg","release_date":"2024-10-07","vote_average":6.753,"backdrop_path":"/9Xx0BCkxDsF47niAPsb8lQ0O9Qu.jpg","original_title":"La habitación de al lado","original_language":"es"}],"similar_content":[{"id":653598,"adult":false,"title":"Spree","video":false,"overview":"Desperate for an online following, a rideshare driver has figured out a deadly plan to go viral and he will stop at nothing to get his five minutes of fame.","genre_ids":[35,80,27,53],"popularity":2.4794,"vote_count":528,"poster_path":"/tbYvzpy4QFhUHRBHe4VeUKJst96.jpg","release_date":"2020-08-14","vote_average":6.408,"backdrop_path":"/2wKOO39vOvWK1vBDb72NuNfkE55.jpg","original_title":"Spree","original_language":"en"},{"id":271078,"adult":false,"title":"Georgia","video":false,"overview":"A young woman investigates the death of her mother, who drowned when her daughter was still a baby. The question is: was it murder, suicide or merely an accident?","genre_ids":[53,9648],"popularity":0.1955,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/fr5WE4UXp50G41idexZ32EFZHBp.jpg","release_date":"1989-10-12","vote_average":1,"backdrop_path":"/1UNQvI7iGjcifmieoxXv34S9Swt.jpg","original_title":"Georgia","original_language":"en"},{"id":1058521,"adult":false,"title":"Still Life","video":false,"overview":"A detective slowly unravels as a serial killer taunts him with depictions of his gruesome crimes.","genre_ids":[27,9648,80],"popularity":0.1388,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/adV0Jnlq4A9obQ4ogubuG3k3cdv.jpg","release_date":"2023-04-01","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Still Life","original_language":"en"},{"id":467363,"adult":false,"title":"Sins of the Past","video":false,"overview":"A ring of call girls leaves the \"business\" when one of them is murdered. The survivors change their names and leave town. However, they are reunited 15 years later when another one of them is murdered and the rest realize that they are all being tracked by the same serial killer.","genre_ids":[9648,53,10770],"popularity":0.2367,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/hqpFy1lgCzGWAqjYzixJPwcQRhE.jpg","release_date":"1984-04-02","vote_average":4,"backdrop_path":"/qi9TJbCPh1cteqEkpJIg27vABwf.jpg","original_title":"Sins of the Past","original_language":"en"},{"id":3050,"adult":false,"title":"Doctor Dolittle","video":false,"overview":"A successful physician and devoted family man, John Dolittle seems to have the world by the tail, until a long suppressed talent he possessed as a child, the ability to communicate with animals is suddenly reawakened with a vengeance! Now every creature within squawking distance wants the good doctor's advice, unleashing an outrageous chain of events that turns his world upside down!","genre_ids":[35,10751,14],"popularity":3.7736,"vote_count":3236,"poster_path":"/tLrchGMIkdo1KamQJA6fwvDQEy0.jpg","release_date":"1998-06-26","vote_average":5.716,"backdrop_path":"/kqUjxYB209bPN0DpfXZuR9E4ERW.jpg","original_title":"Doctor Dolittle","original_language":"en"},{"id":2974,"adult":false,"title":"The Hands of Orlac","video":false,"overview":"A world-famous pianist loses both hands in an accident. When new hands are grafted on, he is horrified to learn they once belonged to a murderer.","genre_ids":[27,53,9648],"popularity":0.9817,"vote_count":107,"poster_path":"/40WWy1SSx8rh1r4mn1MNpCKIteF.jpg","release_date":"1924-09-24","vote_average":6.846,"backdrop_path":"/35Bh31PwHD1c4QoF5Otn1Tpm7I9.jpg","original_title":"Orlacs Hände","original_language":"de"},{"id":2990,"adult":false,"title":"Pacific Heights","video":false,"overview":"A couple works hard to renovate their dream house and become landlords to pay for it. Unfortunately one of their tenants has plans of his own.","genre_ids":[53,18,9648],"popularity":3.2174,"vote_count":404,"poster_path":"/9iHD6xIrGSuuMEFWhwSVGXSddY2.jpg","release_date":"1990-09-28","vote_average":6.252,"backdrop_path":"/duelwmJcXTeEs2huscpxZ97QqOx.jpg","original_title":"Pacific Heights","original_language":"en"},{"id":3176,"adult":false,"title":"Battle Royale","video":false,"overview":"In the future, the Japanese government captures a class of ninth-grade students and forces them to kill each other under the revolutionary \"Battle Royale\" act.","genre_ids":[18,53,28],"popularity":4.7403,"vote_count":3730,"poster_path":"/aLGKAQKgzWpJ6egyWzzC11jXBRJ.jpg","release_date":"2000-12-16","vote_average":7.269,"backdrop_path":"/amBvmIshdsSkOtvVIgxl7YSQ9Dg.jpg","original_title":"バトル・ロワイアル","original_language":"ja"},{"id":276902,"adult":false,"title":"Cut Bank","video":false,"overview":"25-year-old Dwayne McLaren, a former athlete turned auto mechanic, dreams of getting out of tiny Cut Bank, Montana the coldest town in America. But his effort to do so sets in motion a deadly series of events that change his life and the life of the town forever...","genre_ids":[80,18,9648,53],"popularity":0.6253,"vote_count":346,"poster_path":"/hP5N3R8qqe7JT4N3esgh23GOpCN.jpg","release_date":"2014-10-04","vote_average":5.76,"backdrop_path":"/lGoyDkKafXvKmZ2oQYdVMOzuhSX.jpg","original_title":"Cut Bank","original_language":"en"},{"id":6949,"adult":false,"title":"What's Up, Doc?","video":false,"overview":"The accidental mix-up of four identical plaid overnight bags leads to a series of increasingly wild and wacky situations.","genre_ids":[35,80,10749],"popularity":2.8097,"vote_count":439,"poster_path":"/d5WwZxneeAH2Kj2SeDV6oUY2oW0.jpg","release_date":"1972-03-09","vote_average":7.356,"backdrop_path":"/lDeH6UkNGX2UcaOKTJ5SHtmNwbD.jpg","original_title":"What's Up, Doc?","original_language":"en"},{"id":6951,"adult":false,"title":"Turner & Hooch","video":false,"overview":"Detective Scott Turner has three days left in the local police department before he moves to a bigger city to get some 'real' cases—not just misdemeanors. When Amos Reed is murdered, Scott sets himself on the case, but the closest thing to a witness to the murder is Reed's dog, Hooch, which Scott has to take care of—to avoid Hooch being 'put to sleep'.","genre_ids":[28,35,53,80,10751],"popularity":1.9934,"vote_count":1402,"poster_path":"/nllMNbjgvUpw378czm5vBYzZqg1.jpg","release_date":"1989-07-28","vote_average":6.335,"backdrop_path":"/yGCAyKBiHIuM9IdqjxhJ1BhbAgV.jpg","original_title":"Turner & Hooch","original_language":"en"},{"id":470229,"adult":false,"title":"Summer of 84","video":false,"overview":"After suspecting that their police officer neighbor is a serial killer, a group of teenage friends spend their summer spying on him and gathering evidence, but as they get closer to discovering the truth, things get dangerous.","genre_ids":[18,27,9648],"popularity":1.5328,"vote_count":1437,"poster_path":"/zastd8zM2ftOJpC7Y6gRFqAB7r.jpg","release_date":"2018-08-10","vote_average":6.913,"backdrop_path":"/iEYDBciiuW68Q5bLCzkVBgKnfi7.jpg","original_title":"Summer of 84","original_language":"en"},{"id":6978,"adult":false,"title":"Big Trouble in Little China","video":false,"overview":"Truck driver Jack Burton gets embroiled in a supernatural battle when his best friend Wang Chi's green-eyed fiancée is kidnapped by henchmen of the sorcerer Lo Pan, who must marry a girl with green eyes in order to return to the human realm.","genre_ids":[28,35,14,12],"popularity":4.4653,"vote_count":3259,"poster_path":"/gI2Qs1yTTj3NcESJyttCkbmJ4k9.jpg","release_date":"1986-05-30","vote_average":7.207,"backdrop_path":"/ehHskGgDUchxGyG33vUQZWNng43.jpg","original_title":"Big Trouble in Little China","original_language":"en"},{"id":7007,"adult":false,"title":"Rising Sun","video":false,"overview":"When a prostitute is found dead in a Los Angeles skyscraper occupied by a large Japanese corporation, detectives John Connor and Web Smith are called in to investigate. Although Connor has previous experience working in Japan, cultural differences make their progress difficult until a security disc showing the murder turns up. Close scrutiny proves the disc has been doctored, and the detectives realize they're dealing with a cover-up as well.","genre_ids":[28,18,53],"popularity":1.4943,"vote_count":817,"poster_path":"/jVWEeZ383peKxwE284AdyHqq6GH.jpg","release_date":"1993-07-30","vote_average":6.138,"backdrop_path":"/dmaLmrP3PYfhb8P2SWMucZCZqjk.jpg","original_title":"Rising Sun","original_language":"en"},{"id":7183,"adult":false,"title":"Perfect Stranger","video":false,"overview":"A journalist goes undercover to ferret out businessman Harrison Hill as her best friend's killer. Posing as one of his temps, she enters into a game of online cat-and-mouse.","genre_ids":[53,80,9648],"popularity":1.6144,"vote_count":998,"poster_path":"/i7D5QqQ0q5EXU1UuZVY9KwIxoYR.jpg","release_date":"2007-04-11","vote_average":5.829,"backdrop_path":"/sNhYDvDbEwf9AUGip2fGRwP7x8r.jpg","original_title":"Perfect Stranger","original_language":"en"},{"id":7091,"adult":false,"title":"Vampire's Kiss","video":false,"overview":"A publishing executive is visited and bitten by a vampire and starts exhibiting erratic behavior. He pushes his secretary to extremes as he tries to come to terms with his affliction.","genre_ids":[35,27,80,14],"popularity":2.1527,"vote_count":472,"poster_path":"/bEwvlXvvrVLPFwCOND5E38qly01.jpg","release_date":"1989-06-02","vote_average":5.918,"backdrop_path":"/rrmavNBz1aKSY11jbGGnj1Q5CTo.jpg","original_title":"Vampire's Kiss","original_language":"en"},{"id":7281,"adult":false,"title":"The Trixxer","video":false,"overview":"A mysterious serial killer is shocking the underworld. Scotland Yard is investigating the case. Clues lead the detectives to Blackwhite Castle.","genre_ids":[35,80],"popularity":1.4712,"vote_count":227,"poster_path":"/tHcKs8FBYsxxHV3COhBM2EsY0eL.jpg","release_date":"2004-05-20","vote_average":6.383,"backdrop_path":"/lisILqhRqF9qlkFbLVTo6S4Rvbf.jpg","original_title":"Der Wixxer","original_language":"de"},{"id":592,"adult":false,"title":"The Conversation","video":false,"overview":"A paranoid, secretive surveillance expert has a crisis of conscience when he suspects that the couple he is spying on will be murdered.","genre_ids":[80,18,9648],"popularity":2.0821,"vote_count":1982,"poster_path":"/dHqVBwcv1SGymOpUueRoKzcmdes.jpg","release_date":"1974-04-12","vote_average":7.5,"backdrop_path":"/fVJZYpzVTKo0vXmar9NnRMV0Qcn.jpg","original_title":"The Conversation","original_language":"en"},{"id":635,"adult":false,"title":"Angel Heart","video":false,"overview":"A down-a